00:01:41.800 --> 00:01:42.720
What are you looking at?

00:01:42.762 --> 00:01:44.550
♪Twenty years forsaken,
I lived the life of an outlaw♪

00:01:44.720 --> 00:01:45.440
I...

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:46.920
I was wondering

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:48.840
when you'd wake up from your nap,

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:50.440
Scarlet Flame Divine Hog.

00:01:53.075 --> 00:01:55.160
♪Bit by bit,
reality shatters my only hope♪

00:01:55.160 --> 00:01:56.600
I was kidding.

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:57.800
Don't be mad.

00:01:58.612 --> 00:02:03.900
♪Layer by layer, cold blades roll up
the light I once glimpsed in secret♪

00:02:03.960 --> 00:02:05.040
Are you angry?

00:02:05.087 --> 00:02:07.500
♪Letters have long since yellowed♪

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:09.200
Well,

00:02:09.200 --> 00:02:10.480
you're messing with me again, huh?

