00:02:45.080 --> 00:02:46.320
Not... Not this trick again.

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:48.920
I'm killing two birds

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:50.840
with one stone here.

00:02:51.212 --> 00:02:54.350
♪While you rest beneath the earth♪

00:02:54.425 --> 00:02:57.712
♪My love lingers in this frosty world♪

00:02:58.200 --> 00:03:02.850
♪How are you now?♪

00:03:03.560 --> 00:03:04.800
Your heart is pounding.

00:03:06.160 --> 00:03:07.680
So is yours.

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:11.160
That's because my heart is close to you.

00:03:11.225 --> 00:03:17.500
♪How are you now?♪

00:04:05.310 --> 00:04:06.240
Have you thought it through?

00:04:41.640 --> 00:04:43.160
Tomorrow's the Day of Xihe.

00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:45.880
I will fulfill our promise

00:04:46.200 --> 00:04:47.820
and remove the seal off
the Scarlet Flame Clan.

00:04:49.080 --> 00:04:50.560
The Land of Scarlet Flame

00:04:50.560 --> 00:04:52.080
shall be as vital as before.

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:54.298
♪The autumn wind
stirs ripples on the lake♪

00:04:54.300 --> 00:04:58.180
♪I never saw
the promised sea of blossoms♪

00:04:58.880 --> 00:05:00.280
Yet there's no perfection

00:05:00.440 --> 00:05:02.160
in this world.

00:05:03.320 --> 00:05:05.000
There's a price to everything.

00:05:05.787 --> 00:05:09.550
♪What we lived was never written,
only carried in the heart♪

00:05:09.625 --> 00:05:12.662
♪I sigh,
for all beings are bound by fate♪

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.080
When it's all over,

00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:16.200
you must check out
this prosperous world

00:05:16.200 --> 00:05:17.600
and the vast galaxy

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:18.560
on my behalf.

00:05:19.640 --> 00:05:21.640
Experience every sunrise and sunset,

00:05:21.880 --> 00:05:22.880
every dawn and dusk.

00:05:24.520 --> 00:05:25.280
